    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in concours-level condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this specimen, from its unblemished exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free cabin, reflects a history of meticulous maintenance and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. This is a benchmark example of the model, prepared to meet the most exacting standards.",
