    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am absolutely in love with this car, but it's time for it to find a new garage to call home! Honestly, it's in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for your next big adventure. You've really got to see it to believe how clean it is! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
