    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of BMW M division engineering. This specimen features the S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and six individual throttle bodies. This unit has undergone a comprehensive mechanical vetting, including a documented VANOS system refresh and proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag six-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible paint imperfections, while the interior leather maintains its original matte finish and structural bolster integrity. This is a mechanically superlative example, free of typical E46-era wear, offering a pure, high-compression driving experience for the discerning collector.",
